{"about_the_game":"Defense of the Dauntless is an endless horde mode tower defense game with roguelite progression. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923180/extras/description_banner1.png?t=1732811578\" /><br><strong>Build your Defenses, your Way</strong><br>Let your creativity and ingenuity guide where you place your towers and walls. Anything goes!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923180/extras/description_banner2.png?t=1732811578\" /><br><strong>Defend and Reinforce your Stronghold</strong><br>As you defeat the hordes you'll earn reinforcements. These timely bonuses could give you some much needed gold, stun enemies, unlock new tower types, or \u2014\u00a0if you're feeling risky \u2014\u00a0reward you handsomely, for a price. The higher your level, the higher your chances of getting stroner gold and prismatic reinforcements.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923180/extras/description_banner3.png?t=1732811578\" /><br><strong>Survive and Become Dauntless</strong><br>The enemy forces are relentless and will stop at nothing to see your stronghold destroyed. Do you have what it takes to remain <i>dauntless</i>? Enemies appear in constant waves, some with unique defenses and abilities of their own, so be ever-vigilant.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2923180/extras/description_banner4.png?t=1732811578\" /><br><strong>Upgrade your Tower Arsenal</strong><br>Research and unlock progressively more powerful towers between runs to ensure victory! As you unlock towers, new more powerful tiers will be revealed.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Unlocked Arcane Tower","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2923180/6203eb8e2fd6c8231b0ea5d9fd0b835d0b286270.jpg"}